    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it feels like a weight i can't ever put down. i look at the bed and i just... i think about how easy it would be to just stop. to just drift off and not have to worry about breathing or eating or being \"okay\" ever again. it feels like the only actual peace left is just not existing.",
